message.body: Hey. Good morning!
hi!
How's your day?
getting through my Monday .. and you?
Okay. Was out of town all weekend. San Francisco. Met up with someone I haven't seen in years...that was...ummmm...interesting.
lol. sounds like it! we were exploring southeast Colorado all weekend -- would have loved to be in san fran instead!!
We talked about going to Colorado! Weird... May I ask what the "t" stands for?
tina :)
Hey, Tina...i'm angel. ;-)
hi! :)
I think I may've asked this before, but...what city are you in? I'm in Tucson for one more week, then Los Angeles.
Denver. well, actually Aurora, CO (sadly we are now "on the map" and a recognizable name...)
What do you do?
I'm an assistant in ophthalmology (medical eye docs)
Cool. Seriously. I find that stuff fascinating. How long have you been doing it? Do you enjoy it?
6 years and I love it cause I work in a pediatric practice
That sounds awesome!
what do you do?
I'm a musician/engineer and artist. In fact, i'm on my way to tattoo someone right now. My CD is almost done... What kind of music do you like?
awesome! I listen to all kinds of things. what is your cd of??
My band, smothermachine, is dark/alternative. Like if the cure and social distortion had a baby. ;-) It's mostly love songs, honestly... Nothing says
love like a distorted guitar! :-p
